quran[246]{c,v,t}:
  41,47,"Ko ka Makko woni ko ganndal Darngal ruttetee. DimЙ—e yaltataa e coomЙ—i mun, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal Makko.Г‘alnde O noddiroyta Й“e:\"Ko honto woni kafidaaЙ—i Am Й—in?\", Й“e wi'a:\"Men anndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotooЙ—o [Й—um]"
  41,48,ЖҒe majjira e kon ko Й“e rewaynoo ko adii; Й“e yananee wonnde daЙ—irgal alanaa Й“e
  41,49,"NeЙ—Й—anke on haaЙ“ataa toragol moЖҙЖҙere. Si bone memii mo, ko o taЖҙotooЙ—o, yonndiniiЙ—o"
  41,50,"Si Men meeЙ—inir mo moЖҙЖҙere immorde ka Amen, Й“aawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: \"ЖҠum Й—oo ko min ! Mi fellitaani si Darngal daroto. Si mi ruttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, moЖҙЖҙere hino woodani lam ka Makko\". Ma Men humpitu yedduЙ“e Й“en, fii ko Й“e huuwi kon, ko ma Men meeЙ—inoy Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  41,51,"Si Men neeminii e neЙ—Й—anke on, o Й—uurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non heЙ“ii mo, o wona jom toraare yaajunde"
  41,52,"Maaku: \"Yeetee lam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti yedduЙ—on nde; haray ko hommbo Й“uri majjude on wonЙ—o e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal"
  41,53,"Aray Men holla Й“e maandeeji Amen Й—in ka tatteeji e maЙ“Й“e tigi, haa Й“anngana Й“e wonnde ko nde goonga. E yonaali wonnde Joomi maa, ko O seediiЙ—o kala huunde"
  41,54,"Anndee hiЙ“e e sikke fii hawroygol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e. Anndee non, ko O huЙ“indiiЙ—o kala huunde"
  42,1,"Haa, Miim"
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf"
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah TeЙ—Й—uЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On wahayiniri e maa, e Й“en adinooЙ“e ma"
  42,4,"Ko Kanko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko kadi woni ToowuЙ—o, MawЙ—o On"
  42,5,"Kammuuli Й—in no eЙ“Й“a seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e insinanoo wonЙ“e ka leydi Й“en. Anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  42,6,"ЖҒen non jogitiiЙ“e yiЙ—Й“e goo gaanin Makko, Allah ko reenuЙ—o Й“e. A wonaali reenoowo Й“e"
  42,7,"Ko wano non Men wahayniri e maaЙ—a, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jertin yimЙ“e neene ca'e Й—en e wonЙ“e takko mayre Й“en, jertinaa fii Гұalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'un - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite"
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O waЙ—ayno Й“e mofte goote. Kono himo On mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende Makko. TooГұooЙ“e Й“en non, giЙ—o alanaa Й“e, wanaa ballo"
  42,9,"Kaa Й“e jogiti yiЙ—Й“e goo gaanin Makko? Awa ko Allah woni GiЙ—o On, ko Kanko wuurnitata maayЙ“e Й“en; ko Kanko kadi woni kaЙ—tanЙ—o kala huunde"
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondirЙ—on e fii mun, haray Гұaawoore mun nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko On mooЙ—on Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]"
  42,11,"FuЙ—Й—uЙ—o kamuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. O waЙ—iranii on e pittaali mon Й—in genndooЙ“e, ka neemoraaЙ—i kadi nooneeji; Himo Й—uЙ—Й—inira on Й—um. Hay huunde yerondiraa e Makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  42,12,"Ko Kanko heerori soktirЙ—e kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo wertana arsike on mo O muuyani, O Й“iЙ—tinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, konko ko O yamirnoo Nuuhu, e kon ko Men wahayini e maaЙ—a, e kon ko Men yamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, wonnde: \"Г‘iЙ“nee diina kan; hara on seertaali e makka\". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkooЙ“e Й“en e mun kon, mawnii e dow maЙ“Й“e. Allah non hino suЙ“anoo Й—um, mo O muuyani, O fewna e Makko, kala tuuboowo"
  42,14,"ЖҒe seertaano, si wanaa Й“aawo nde ganndal ngal arde e maЙ“Й“e, sabu bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Si wanaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal taЖҙaangal, Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Ko pellet, roninaaaЙ“e Deftere nden Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitiiЙ“e"
  42,15,"Noddu (yimЙ“e Й“en) kisan; ГұiiЙ“iraa no yamiraЙ—aa non, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, maakaa: \"Mi gomЙ—inii ko Allah jippini kon (fow) e Defte, mi yamiraama kadi, nunЙ—ugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah mooЙ“oyay e denndaandal. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  42,16,"ЖҒen wennjirooЙ“e e diina Allah kan, Й“aawo ka jaЙ“aneede, hujja maЙ“Й“e on ko meere, tikkere no fawii e maЙ“Й“e, hino woodani Й“e kadi lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri Deftere nden goonga, e manndakke Й—en. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara Darngal ngal ko ko Й“adii"
  42,18,"ЖҒeya Й“e gomЙ—inaali ngal Й“en, hiЙ“e heГұoringal; gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en kan, ko Й“e hulu fii maggal, e hoore hiЙ“e felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee wonЙ“e yeddondireede Й“en fii Darngal, ko pellet, Й“e wonii e nder majjere woЙ—Й—unde"
  42,19,"Allah ko newaniiЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Himo arsike on mo O muuyani. Ko Kanko woni DoolnuЙ—o, FooluЙ—o On"
  42,20,"Kala tawЙ—o ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men Й“eydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi tawЙ—o ko jayru ndun aduna o yiЙ—i, Men okkay mo Й—um, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) geЙ“al"
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaaЙ—i hino woodani Й“e, sar'inanЙ—i Й“e e diina kan, kon ko Allah duЕӢaaki fii mun? Si wanaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde maЙ“Й“e], Гұaaweteno hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Ko pellet, hino woodani tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, lepte muusuЙ—e"
  42,22,"A yi'ay tooГұuЙ“e Й“en hino huli e ko Й“e fggitii kon, Й—um le ko yantayЙ—um e maЙ“Й“e. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hiЙ“e e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kala ko Й“e faaletee. Ko Й—um tigiri, woni Й“ural mawnungal ngal"
  42,23,"Ko Й—um woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaaЙ“e Makko gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe. Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njoЙ“di e Й—um, si wanaa tun giggol enЙ—am Й—am\". Kala faggitiiЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere, Men Й“eydanay mo moЖҙЖҙere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, mantoowo"
  42,24,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notayno e Й“ernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol Makko ngol. Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o gunndooji Й“erЙ—e Й—en"
  42,25,"Ko Kanko woni jaЙ“anoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bonЙ—i Й—in, e hoore Himo anndi ko golloton kon"
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i, O Й“eydana Й“e e Й“ural Makko ngal. HeeferЙ“e Й“en non, hino woodani Й“e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e"
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah yaГұГұanno jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en [fow] arsike, pellet, Й“e bewayno ka leydi; kono Himo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O HummpitiiЙ—o, yi*oowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo toЙ“o ngon Й“aawo Й“e taЖҙaade, O saaka yurmeende Makko nden. Ko Kanko kadi woni GiЙ—o, YettiniiЙ—o On"
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e ruugayЙ—i Й—i O saaki Й—in hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii mooЙ“indiroygol Й“e ngol, si O haajii, ko O hattanЙ—o"
  42,30,"Kala ko heЙ“i on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juuЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko Й—uuЙ—i"
  42,31,"On wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi ; alanaa on gaanin Allah, giЙ—o, wanaa ballo"
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko Й—in: dogayЙ—e Й—en ka maayo, wa'uЙ—e wa pelle"
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O deeЖҙinay henndu ndun, ndu waЙ—tinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji, wonannde kala muГұГұotooЙ—o, yettoowo"
  42,34,Maa yooliraЙ—e sabu ko Й“e faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non ko Й—uuЙ—i
  42,35,"WennjooЙ“e Й“en e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, hino anndi Й“e alaa laaworde"
  42,36,"Kala ko okkaЙ—on e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah kon, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en fawotooЙ“e e Joomi maЙ“Й“e"
  42,37,"woЙ—Й—itotooЙ“e bakkaatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in e pankare Й—en, si wonii Й“e tikkii, hara Й“e yaafoto"
  42,38,"Й“en nootiiЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ГұiЙ“ni julde nden, Й“e tawata fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on ko diisondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, nafqooЙ“e e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e"
  42,39,"e Й“en tawЙ“e si bewre heЙ“ii Й“e, Й“e yottoto"
  42,40,"NjoЙ“di bonnere, ko bone yeru mun. Kala non yaafiiЙ—o o moЖҙЖҙintini, haray njoЙ“di makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiЙ—aa tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  42,41,"Kala non yottiiЙ“e Й“aawo Й“e tooГұeede, ko Й“en woni Й“e laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mun"
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mun, ko tooГұooЙ“e yimЙ“e Й“en, hara hiЙ“e bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: Й“e Й—on, hino woodani lepte muusuЙ—e"
  42,43,"MuГұГұiiЙ—o on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, Й—um no jeyaa e pellital fiyakuujI"
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray giЙ—o (goo) alanaa mo Й“aawo Й—um. A tinay tooГұuЙ“e Й“en, tuma Й“e yi'i lepte Й—en, hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi"
  42,45,"A tinay Й“e kadi, hiЙ“e weeЙ“itee e magge, hara hiЙ“e yankinii koyeera on, hiЙ“e ndaarira ndaarЙ—e leppagol. GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en wi'aya: \"Ko woni hayru Й“e Й“en, ko Й“en hayrimЙ“e ko'e mun e Й“eynguureeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Г‘alnde Darngal\". Anndee pellet, tooГұuЙ“e Й“en no e lepte duumiiЙ—e"
  42,46,"YiЙ—Й“e alanaa Й“e, ko wallitoo Й“e, hara wanaa Allah. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo"
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado Гұalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa Й—um ka Allah. Nden Гұalnde, faaborde alanaa on, yeddugol kadi alanaa on"
  42,48,"Si Й“e Й—uurnike non, haray Men nuliraali ma, aynoowo Й“e: fawaaki ma, si wanaa yottingol. Si wonii Men meeЙ—iniri neЙ—Й—anke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non heЙ“i Й“e, sabu kon ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardiniri, a taway pellet, neЙ—Й—o on ko jedduЙ—o sanne"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko O muuyi. Himo yeЙ—a mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e, O yeЙ—a kadi mo O muuyani Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e"
  42,50,"maa O jillira Й“e worЙ“e e rewЙ“e; Himo waЙ—a dimaro, on mo O muuyani. Pellet, ko O AnnduЙ—o, HaЙ—tanЙ—o"
  42,51,"Sellantaa neЙ—Й—anke, nde Allah yewtata mo, si wanaa wahayu, maa e Й“aawo heedo, maa O immina NulaaЙ—o (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duЕӢayee(sakkitoore) Makko, kon ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O ToowuЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  42,52,"Ko wano non Men wayayinir e maaЙ—a, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Deftere, maa gomЙ—inal; si ko woni, Men waЙ—unde ndaygu, ngu Men fewnirta on mo Men muuyani e jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo e laawol focciingol"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jeyЙ—o ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji Й—in ruttotoo"
  43,1,"Haa, Miim"
  43,2,Mi woondirii Defere Й“anngunde nden
  43,3,"Men waЙ—ii nde janngeteende [e Й—emngal] aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  43,4,"Pellet, hinde woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma Defte, toowunde, ГұeГұaande"
  43,5,"E Men acciray jippinangol on jantoore nden, Й—uurngal on, fii on wonii yimЙ“e fantimЙ“e"
  43,6,ЖҠuuЙ—ii e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“e Men nuli e adinooЙ“e Й“en
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“e jalkitay mo"
  43,8,Men halki ko Й“uri Й“e saЙ—tude doole ! Toode mise adinooЙ“e Й“en yawtiino
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin?\" ЖҒe wi'ay: \"Ko FooluЙ—o, AnnduЙ—o On tagi Й—i"
  43,10,"On waЙ—iranЙ—o on leydi ndin weertaandi, O waЙ—ani on Й—ate e mayri, fii no Й—oworon"
  43,11,"On jippinrЙ—o toЙ“o ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Men wuurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko non yaltinirteЙ—on"
  43,12,"On taguЙ—o nooneeji Й—in fow, O waЙ—irani on e laaЙ—e Й—en e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ko waЙ—Й—oron"
  43,13,"fii yo on fotondir e hoore majji, refti annditon neema Joomi mon On, tuma fotondirЙ—on e majji, wi'on ontuma: \"Senayee woodanii eltanЙ—o men Й—um On, men wonaano taaqanaaЙ“e Й—um"
  43,14,"menen non, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko men ruttotoo"
  43,15,"ЖҒe waЙ—ani Mo geЙ“al e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en ! Pellet, on neЙ—Й—anke ko yedduЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e Й“en"
  43,17,"Si goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e wewliniraama ko o waЙ—irani kon Hinaranke On misal, yeeso makko ngon niЙ“Й“ita metteendi hombo suuЙ—i"
  43,18,"E ko on ne'eteeЙ—o e cuЙ—aari, hara kanko on ka yeddondiral, wanaa o Й“annginoowo haala"
  43,19,"ЖҒe waЙ—i Malaa'ikaaЙ“e tawЙ“e Й“en ko jeyaaЙ“e Jom Hinaranke On, rewЙ“e ! Kere Й“e seedino tageede Й“en? Awa fii seedagol maЙ“Й“e ngol winndete, Й“e lamnditoyee"
  43,20,"ЖҒe wi'iti: \"Si Jom Hinaranke On haajuno, men rewataano Й“e\". ЖҒe alanaa Й—um hay e ganndal; Й“e wonaali, si wanaa hiЙ“e fena"
  43,21,"Kaa ko Deftere Men addani Й“e ado ndee Й—oo, hara ko nden woni ko Й“e jogitii"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, Й“e wi'iu: \"Menen men tawu baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en e diina, haray ko e batteeji maЙ“Й“e men feewirta"
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Men nulaali jertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wanaa hooreeЙ“e maЙ“Й“e neemiiЙ“e wi'ay: \"Menen men tawu baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en e diina, Й—um non ko batteeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in men Гұentinta"
  43,24,"O maaki: \"Hay si mi addan on ko Й“uri feewude kon ko tawruЙ—on baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en?\" ЖҒe wi'i: \"Menen dey, ko men yedduЙ“e ko nulidaЙ—on e mun kon"
  43,25,Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e. ndaare no battande fennuЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo
  43,26,"Janto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: \"Min on ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e kon ko rewoton"
  43,27,"si wanaa On taguЙ—o lam, Kanko On, O fewnay lam"
  43,28,"O waЙ—i ngol konngol heddotoongol Й“aawo makko, belajo'o, Й“e ruttoto"
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii Й“ee Й—oo e baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, haa nde goonga kan arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, e NulaaЙ—o Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arunoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'i: \"ЖҠum ko mbilewu, menen ko men yedduЙ“e Й—um"
  43,31,"ЖҒe wi'iti: \"Ko hanno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko mawЙ—o ca'e Й—en Й—iЙ—i"
  43,32,"E ko kamЙ“e senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi nguureeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, ka nguurndam aduna. Men Й“amti yoga maЙ“Й“e e hoore Й“eya, darjaaji, fii no yoga maЙ“Й“e jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa nden, Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e kon ko Й“e mooЙ“ata"
  43,33,"Si wanaano fii wata yimЙ“e Й“en wonu mofte goote, Men waЙ—ayno e cuuЙ—i kala yedduЙ—o Hinnaranke On: kiЙ“Й“e kaalisi e ЕӢabbirЙ—e ka Й“e Жҙawra"
  43,34,"(Men waЙ—ayno kadi) e cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, dame e ndaЙ—Й—ude ka Й“e soЙ“Й“indoo"
  43,35,"e cuЙ—aari. Kono Й—um fow wonaali, si wanaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko laakara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gomЙ—umЙ“e Й“en"
  43,36,"Kala Й—uurniiЙ—o e jantoore Hinaranko On, Men wuurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata"
  43,37,"ЖҠin (awaseeji) non, ko sakkorayЙ—i Й“e e peewal ngal, haa ka Й“e sikkata hiЙ“e feewi"
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amen, o wi'a: \"Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa woЙ—Й—irayno goЙ—Й—al fuЙ—Й—irЙ—e Й—en Й—iЙ—i woЙ—Й—iri ! A bonii cinndadiiЙ—o"
  43,39,"[ЖҠum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on tooГұii - wonnde ko ka lepte hawtuЙ—on"
  43,40,E ko an naninta faaЙ—uЙ—o maa fewnaa bumЙ—o e on wonЙ—o e nder majjere Й“anngunde
  43,41,"Si Men aru Жҙettitude ma, haray ko Men yottotooЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e"
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Men kammbirani Й“en kon, haray noon ko Men gaynooЙ“e fii maЙ“Й“e"
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a. Pellet, hiЙ—a jokki laawol focciingol"
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yimЙ“e maa Й“en. Aray nde lamnditeЙ—on"
  43,45,"Lamndii e Й“en NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“e Men nulunoo ado maa, si Men waЙ—uno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, reweteeЙ—i goo"
  43,46,"GomЙ—ii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: \"Ko mi NulaaЙ—o JeyЙ—o tagu ngun"
  43,47,"Nde o addannooЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, e jaka yoo hiЙ“e jalaЙ—i"
  43,48,"Men hollaali Й“e Aaya, si wanaa haray on Й“uri adiiЙ—o mo on mawnude. Men nanngiri Й“e lepte Й—en, belajo'o, Й“e ruttoto"
  43,49,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano men Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maaЙ—a. Pellet, ko men feewooЙ“e"
  43,50,"Nde Men huncannooЙ“e lepte Й—en, e jaka yoo, hiЙ“e firta [ahadi]"
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yimЙ“e Й“en, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, wanaa min jey laamu Misra? E hino Й—ii canЙ—i no ila e ley kuЙ“eeji am? E on yiyataa"
  43,52,Kaa mi Й“uraa teddude oo hoyЙ—o mo eЙ“Й“ataa laЙ“Й“innde haala
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawle kaЕӢЕӢe werlee e makko? MaaЙ—um Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri"
  43,54,"O Й—aytini yimЙ“e makko Й“en, Й“e Й—owtii mo. Pellet, Й“en Й—on laatino yimЙ“e faasiqiiЙ“e"
  43,55,"Nde Й“e tikkinnoo Men, Men yottii e maЙ“Й“e; Men yooli Й“e fow"
  43,56,"Men waЙ—i Й“e ardiiЙ“e e misal, wonannde sakkiitiiЙ“e Й“en"
  43,57,"Tuma nde geЙ—al neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yimЙ“e maa Й“en no sooЖҙira Й—um"
  43,58,"Й“e wi'i: \"Ko reweteeЙ—i amen Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude, kaa ko kanko?\" ЖҒe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wanaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko Й“e yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e wennje"
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaali, si wanaa jeyaaЙ—o mo Men neemini e mun, Men waЙ—i mo misal woannde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  43,60,"Si Men haajuno, Men waЙ—titirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi"
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wata on sikkito fii maggal. Jokkee lam, ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,62,"Wata seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o gaГұo mon Й“annguЙ—o"
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e Й“annguЙ—i Й—in, o maaki: \"GomЙ—ii mi ardanii on e ГұeeГұal, e no mi Й“annginirana on yoga e ko luutondirЙ—on e muuЙ—um. Haray hulee Allah, Й—oftoЙ—on mi"
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Rewee Mo. Ko Й—um woni laawol focciingol ngol"
  43,65,"Feddeeji Й—in luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, immorde e lepte Гұalaande muusuЙ—e"
  43,66,"Hara Й“e habbi si wanaa nde Darngal ngal ardata Й“e e juhal, hara Й“e so'aa anndude"
  43,67,"WelduЙ“e Й“en, nden Гұalnde, yoga maЙ“Й“e ko ayrooЙ“e yoga; si wanaa gomЙ—umЙ“e Й“en"
  43,68,Ko onon yo jeyaaЙ“e Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotooЙ“e kadi
  43,69,"Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, Й“e woni jebbiliiЙ“e"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nannduЙ“e e mon, hiЙ—on saЙ—nee"
  43,71,"[GollooЙ“e] hino wanngindinee e maЙ“Й“e, mirannji kaЕӢЕӢe e ГұedduЙ—e; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotooЙ“e ton"
  43,72,"Ko on woni Aljanna mo roniniraЙ—on, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  43,73,"Hino woodani on ton, muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i, Й—i Гұaamoton e mun"
  43,74,"Pellet, bomЙ“e Й“en, ko ka lepte Jahannama Й“e luttoyta"
  43,75,"Й“e hoynantaake, tee hara ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e ton"
  43,76,"Men tooГұaani Й“e few, si ko woni, ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  43,77,"ЖҒe nodda: \"Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !\" O wi'i: \"Pellet, ko on luttooЙ“e [ton]"
  43,78,"GomЙ—ii Men addanii on goonga kan ; kono Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e e mon, ko aГұuЙ“e goonga"
  43,79,Kaa Й“e eЙ“Й“u feere ? Doo ko Men fewjooЙ“e
  43,80,Maa hara Й“e sikku Men nanataa gunndooji maЙ“Й“e e sirru maЙ“Й“e? OoвҖҷowoye! NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en hino maandina takko maЙ“Й“e
  43,81,"Maaku: \"Si Hinaranko On no jogitii Й“iЙ—Й—o, ko min adotonoo rewude on"
  43,82,"Senayee woodanii JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, JeyЙ—o Arsi kin; laaЙ“uЙ—o e kon ko Й“e sifrotta Mo. @Corrected"
  43,83,"AccuЙ“e Й“e jumpa, Й“e fija haa Й“e hawroya e Гұalaande maЙ“Й“e ndeЙ“e fodaa"
  43,84,"Ko Kanko woni On reweteeЙ—o ka kammu e reweteeЙ—o ka leydi, ko Kanko kadi woni Г‘eeГұo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  43,85,"Barke heewanii On Mo woodani Й—um, laamu kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka Makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka Makko kadi rutteteЙ—on"
  43,86,"ЖҠi Й“e rewata Й—in gaanin Makko jeyah tefoore, si wanaa seediiЙ“e goonga Й“en, hara hiЙ“e anndi"
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike Й“e, ko hommbo woni ko tagi Й“e? ЖҒe wi'ay: \"Ko Allah\". Ko honno non Й“e yiiliraa"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (NulaaЙ—o) on maakunoo kon: \"Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, Й“ee ko yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—intaa"
  43,89,"Awa yaafo Й“e, maakaa: \"Kisal !\" Aray ndebe annda"
  44,1,"Haa, Miim"
  44,2,Mi woondirii Defere Й“anngunde nden
  44,3,"Men jippinirii nde e jemma barkinaaЙ—o, Men siforii wonde jertinooЙ“e"
  44,4,Ko e on (jemma) woni ko senndetee kala fiyaaku ГұeГұaaЙ—o
  44,5,ЖҠum ko yamiroore immorde ka Amen. Men siforii wonde NulooЙ“e
  44,6,"yurmeende immornde ka Joomi maa. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, AnnduЙ—o On"
  44,7,"JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, si wonii ko on yananaaЙ“e"
  44,8,"ReweteeЙ—o goo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Himo wuurna, Himo wara. JeyЙ—o on Jeyi baabiraaЙ“e mon aramЙ“e Й“en"
  44,9,"Ko woni tun, Й“e wonii e sikke, hiЙ“e fija"
  44,10,Habbito Гұalnde kammu ngun ardata e curki feeГұuuki
  44,11,"suddayki yimЙ“e Й“en. [ЖҒe wi'anee]: \"ЖҠum ko lepte muusuЙ—e"
  44,12,"Joomi amen, huncan men lepte Й—en. Menen ko men gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  44,13,"Ko honno Й“e waajitorta, ko goongo NulaaЙ—o Й“annginЙ—o ariino Й“e"
  44,14,"Refti Й“e hucciti, Й“e wi'i: \"Ko tinndinaaЙ—o, haangaaЙ—o"
  44,15,"Awa ko Men ittooЙ“e lepte Й—en seeЙ—a; kono pellet, ko on ruttitotooЙ“e"
  44,16,"Г‘alnde Men nanngiroyta wippannde mawnde nden, pellet, ko Men yottoytooЙ“e"
  44,17,"GomЙ—ii Men jarribinoke ado maЙ“Й“e, yimЙ“e Fir'awna Й“en, NulaaЙ—o tedduЙ—o ari e maЙ“Й“e"
  44,18,"wonnde: \"WaЙ—ee e juuЙ—e am, jeyaaЙ“e Allah Й“en. Min ko mi NulaaЙ—o e mon, hoolniiЙ—o"
  44,19,"E wonde wata on townitano Allah, tawde mi addanay on hujja Й“annguЙ—o"
  44,20,"Min kadi non, mi moolorii JeyЙ—o lam On Jeyi on, nde fiЙ—otonmi kaaЖҙe"
  44,21,"Si on gomЙ—inaa lam, haray selee lam"
  44,22,"O noddi Joomi makko, wonnde: \"ЖҒee Й—oo, ko yimЙ“e bomЙ“e"
  44,23,Yaadir e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en jemma; anndon ko on cukketeeЙ“e
  44,24,"Accaa maayo ngon deeЖҙa [si on lummbii] Й“eya kan, ko konu yooleteengu"
  44,25,ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko Й“e acci e gese e Й“ulli
  44,26,e remuruuji e koЙ—ande teddunde
  44,27,e neemaaji Й—i Й“e wonunoo e neeminireede
  44,28,Ko wano non. Hooti Men ronini Й—i yimЙ“e goo
  44,29,"Kammu ngun toЙ“aali Й“e, wanaa leydi ndin, Й“e wonaali kadi muГұanteeЙ“e"
  44,30,GomЙ—ii Men daЙ—ndii Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en e lepte hoyneeje
  44,31,"immorde e Fir'awna, tawde o laatino townitiiЙ—o, jeyaaЙ—o e fantimЙ“e Й“en"
  44,32,GomЙ—ii Men suЙ“orike Й“e e dow ganndal e hoore winndere nden
  44,33,"Men okki Й“e maandeeji, Й—i jarrabuyee Й“annguЙ—o woni e mun"
  44,34,ЖҒee kan no wi'a
  44,35,"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa maayde amen aranere nden tun. Men wonatah immintinoyteeЙ“e"
  44,36,"Awa artiree baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en, si wonii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  44,37,"Kere ko kamЙ“e Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kaa ko yimЙ“e \"Tubba'in\" Й“en e Й“eya adinooЙ“e Й“e? Men halkuno Й“en, tawde hari ko Й“e bomЙ“e"
  44,38,"Men tagiraali kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, fijooЙ“e"
  44,39,"Men tagiraali Й—in Й—iЙ—i, si wanaa e goonga. Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e anndaa"
  44,40,"Pellet, ko Г‘alaande Senndindiro ngon, woni ko Й“e saatinanaa, kamЙ“e fof"
  44,41,"Г‘alnde nde giЙ—o duncanoytaa giЙ—o [mun] hay huunde; Й“e wonaali kadi walloyteeЙ“e"
  44,42,"si wanaa mo Allah yurmaa woo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o On"
  44,43,"Pellet, leggal Zaqquumi ngal"
  44,44,ko Гұaametee bakkondimЙ“e Й“en
  44,45,A sikkay ko taayinaa ; hino fata ka nder deedi
  44,46,Wano wulЙ—am fatirta
  44,47,Nanngee mo pooЙ—iron ka hakkunde dulЙ“aynge
  44,48,"refti yuppon ka hoore makko, lepte fatinaaЙ—e Й—en"
  44,49,"MeeЙ—u non ! An [sikkunooЙ—o] ko a fooluЙ—o, tedduЙ—o"
  44,50,Awa ko Й—um woni kon ko sikkitiЙ—on e mum
  44,51,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en wonii e weerde hoolniinde"
  44,52,e nder gese e Й“ulli
  44,53,"hiЙ“e Й“oornoo ko Й—aati e ko tekki, hara hiЙ“e fewtondiri"
  44,54,Ko wano non. Men resini Й“e kadi yaajuЙ“e gite
  44,55,"HiЙ“e nodda toon, kala muuyanteeЙ—i, hara ko Й“e hooliiЙ“e"
  44,56,"ЖҒe meeЙ—ataa ton maayde, si wanaa maayde aranere nden. O daЙ—nda Й“e lepte Jahiimi Й—en"
  44,57,"ko dokkal non, immorde ka Joomi maa. Awa ko Й—um woni maloore mawnde nden"
  44,58,"Ko Men newiniri nde e Й—amngal maaЙ—a, ko no Й“e waajitora"
  44,59,Habiito. KamЙ“e ko Й“e habbitiiЙ“e
  45,1,"Haa, Miim"
  45,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, maandeeji wonannde gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  45,4,"Hino e tagugol on ngol kadi, e kon ko O saaki e ruugayЙ—i, ko maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e yananaaЙ“e Й“en"
  45,5,"E luutondirgol jemma e Гұalorma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e toЙ“o, O wuurnitiri ngo leydi ndin Й“aawo ndi yoorude, e firlitagol keneeli Й—in, ko maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e Й“en"
  45,6,"ЖҠin ko maandeeji Allah Й—i Men janngirante hoore goonga. E ko honЙ—um e yewtere Й“e gomЙ—inta, Й“aawo [yewtere] Allah nden e Aayeeje Makko Й—en"
  45,7,Bone woodanii kala fenoowo bakkondinЙ—o
  45,8,"Mo no nana Aayeeje Allah Й—en hino janngee e dow makko, refti o hedditora e townitaare, wa si tawii o nanaali Й—e. Awa wewlinir mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  45,9,"Si o anndii goЙ—Й—um e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, o jogitora Й—um jalnori. ЖҒen Й—on, hino woodani lepte hoynooje"
  45,10,"Jahannama hino caggal maЙ“Й“e. Ko Й“e faggitinoo duncanoytaaЙ“e hay huunde, wanaa kon ko Й“e jogitinoo yiЙ—Й“e ko wonaa Allah. Hino woodani Й“e lepte mawЙ—e"
  45,11,"Ndee [Deftere]ko peewal. ЖҒen yedduЙ“e non Aayeeje Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hino woodani lepte soЙ“uЙ—e muusuЙ—e"
  45,12,"Ko Alla oon woni ko eeltanta mon maaya ngam laaЙ—e ndoga e hengo e dow yamiroore Makko, ngam Й—aЙ“Й“on e Й“ural Makko e yaama joo njetton"
  45,13,"O eeltani on ko woni e kammuuji e ka leydi fof, wonii e Й—uum kaawisaaji wonande yimЙ“e miijatooЙ“e"
  45,14,Maakan Й“een goonЙ—iЙ“e yoЙ“e njaafa Й“een Й“e tijjaaki nyalЙ—i Alla ngam O yoЙ“a Й“e yimЙ“e koЙ“e paggittono ko
  45,15,"Kala golluЙ—o ko moЖҙЖҙi,ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnuЙ—o,yantay e makko refti ko ka Joomi maa woni ruttorde mon"
  45,16,Min tottii banii Israa*iil deftere e nyeenyal e annabaagal Min njeЙ—iЙ“e e dagiiЙ—i Min Й“urniЙ“e ko heewi e binnde hee
  45,17,Min totti dallillaaji Й“annginooji Й“e luuraani si wonah caggal nde ganndal ari e mum en sabu bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e pellet Jooma na nyaawa hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nyande darnga koЙ“e njeddandiratnoo ko
  45,18,"Refti Min mbaЙ—ma e laawol e yamiroore Amen, woto rew belaaЙ—e Й“een Й“e nganndah"
  45,19,"Pellet Й“een Й“e nafataama gaa e Alla hay huunde pellet toonyooЙ“e yogo e mum en ko weldiiЙ“e, Alla woni keeda hulЙ“e Й“e"
  45,20,O quraana kombo gite e peewal e yurmeende wonande yananaaЙ“e
  45,21,Mbela Й“een waЙ—Й“e boneeji na nanndi e goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e golli golle lobbe hoЙ“e fota e nguurndam mum en e maayde maЙ“Й“e bonii koЙ“e nyaawata
  45,22,Alla tagrii kammuuji e leydi goonga ngam kala fittaandu yoЙ“ee kondu fagginoo ko kamЙ“e Й“e toonyetaake
  45,23,"Mbela a yiyaani oon jaggirЙ—o belaaЙ—e makko deweteeЙ—o Alla majjini mbo e dow ganndal O uddi nanЙ—e makko e Й“ernde makko, O waЙ—i e gite makko hee cuddi ko hombo feewnata oon caggal Alla mate on miiccataaka"
  45,24,"HeeferЙ“e wii Й—um wonah si wonah nguurndam aduna min maaya min nguura, halkataa min si wonah jamaanu, Й“e ngalanah Й—uum ganndal Й“e cikkita tan"
  45,25,Si aayeeje Amen Й“annguЙ—e njanngaama e mum en hujja maЙ“Й“e wonatah si wonah ngaddee baabiraaЙ“e amen si on ngonii goonguЙ“e
  45,26,"Maaku ko Alla wuurnata on refti O wara on refti renndina on faade Гұalawma darnga mbo sikke alah e mum, kono ko Й“uri heewde e yimЙ“e nganndah"
  45,27,"Woodanii Alla laamu kammuuji e leydi, Гұande darnga darii Гұande heen meerenteeЙ“e perta"
  45,28,"HaЙ—a yiya -aan nulaaЙ—a- kala lenyol na gurfanii e koppi mum,kala lenyol na noddiree deftere mum hannde woni ko njoЙ“eteЙ—on ko ngollatnaЙ—on e nder aduna"
  45,29,"Ndee ko deftere amen honde wowla goonga, Min ngoniina Min ceeraani wonde emin njamira nde winndate ko ngollatna Й—on"
  45,30,"Tawi ko Й“een goonЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle lobbe O naatnatЙ“e e yurmeende makko, ko Й—uum woni mala Й“anngungal"
  45,31,Tawi ko Й“een heefareeЙ“e mbela aayeeje Am Й—e njanngetanooke e dow mon mawnikiniЙ—o laatiЙ—on yimЙ“e bonЙ“e
  45,32,"SibЙ“e wiyaama pellet fodoore Alla ko goonga sikke alah heen mbi*on min nganndah ko woni darnga, min cikkiti cikkitagol min ngonaani yananaaЙ“e"
  45,33,"boneeji Й—i Й“e faggitinoo Й—in feГұana Й“e, ko Й“e jalkitaynoo kon fiiltoo Й“e"
  45,34,"Й“e wi*ana hannde Min njejjita mon hono no njejjitirЙ—on pottal Гұalngu mon hannde ngu, ko yiite woni hoЙ—orde mno on ndanyatah walladiiЙ“e"
  45,35,"Й—uum noon ko sabu on njaggarii aayeeje Alla Й—e jalkito nguurndam aduna hoomti on,hannde Й“e njaltatah e yiite Й“e nduttataaka aduna Й“e golla golle lobbe haa Alla weleeЙ“e"
  45,36,Woodanii Alla yettoore nder kammuuji e leydi Jom binnde
  45,37,Na woodani Mbo manngu nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni mbo gooto foolah ГұeeГұuЙ—o